Feature: Default user on fresh install
  In order to be able to set up a fresh install
  As a System administrator
  I want to have access to the application

  In order to be able test a feature on an empty database
  As a Developer
  I want to have access to the application

  Scenario: Started on an empty database, Timeadmin creates a Default user
  Scenario: The Default user can log in with Client and Administration permissions
  Scenario: If the Default user is active, a warning message is displayed on the login page
  Scenario: If the Default user is disabled, no warning message is displayed
